description: This Chainlink VRF common Yulenka purrs with a rating of 44, and a multiplier of 2x. It has a total score of 88, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 3 for North, 5 for East, 8 for South, and 8 for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80442-35884-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [88 Votes, Common]
